snippet.title: Upside Town by Makh-Shevet (English version) עיר-בוביה
snippet.description: This is a short video from the English version of the game "Ir-buvia" made by now-defunct Israeli based company Makh-Shevet and published under the name "Upside-Town" outside of Israel.
